  Sure, I can help you with that! Here's the translation of the English sentence "This has given birth to the NPG to become the owner/operator of Ghana’s first nuclear power plant" into Twi:

Wo da wi so na NPG ni wo sika mmaa afuoo kasa;

Please note that Twi is a tonal language, so the tone marks (á, é, í, ó, ú) are important for accurate pronunciation.</s>

